Hello @yuucyf 

if you import the plug in the agent index.ts remember to not only import abcPlugin but also to add in the sdame file the configuration of the .env elements you need example: 

        case ModelProviderName.AKASH_CHAT_API:
            return (
                character.settings?.secrets?.AKASH_CHAT_API_KEY ||
                settings.AKASH_CHAT_API_KEY
            );
        case ModelProviderName.GOOGLE:
            return (
                character.settings?.secrets?.GOOGLE_GENERATIVE_AI_API_KEY ||
                settings.GOOGLE_GENERATIVE_AI_API_KEY
            );
            
If the .env wil have that keys in and you load the caracter the plugin shuld be active. 
Did you follow this best practice adding your custom code ?
